OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMPs told to smarten up     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftheir clothing ahead of    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FCommons return             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, MPs have been told to smarten up their 
OL,6, clothing when they return from summer  
OL,7, recess to the Commons next week.       
OL,9,FWith the age of the virtual Commons now
OL,10,Fover, Speaker Sir Lindsay Hoyle has    
OL,11,Fupdated the "Rules of behaviour and    
OL,12,Fcourtesies" in the House.              
OL,14,FHe has alerted MPs to required dress   
OL,15,Fstandards, insisting clothing such as  
OL,16,Fjeans and chinos are not allowed.      
OL,18,FIt represents a toughening of the      
OL,19,Fadvice from his predecessor, who said  
OL,20,Fthere was "no exact dress code".       
